@startuml
title Agentic Flow v2.2.0 - Actual Run Flow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Team Lead" as TL
participant "Product Manager" as PM
participant "Java Architect" as ARCH
participant "Reviewer" as REV
participant "Java Coder" as CODER

note over TL,CODER #E2E8F0
Green = passed gate
Yellow = rejected / returned
Red = red card
end note

group Planning Phase
TL -> PM : Story attempt 1
PM --> TL : Story draft
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject story\nrequirement inconsistency

TL -> PM : Story attempt 2
PM --> TL : Updated story
TL -> ARCH : Create plan
ARCH --> TL : Plan ready
TL -> REV : Phase 1 review
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS
end

group Implementation Phase
TL -> CODER : Batch 1
CODER --> TL : Handoff attempt
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject\nmissing summary despite green checks
TL -> CODER : Batch 1 retry
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Accepted batch 1

TL -> CODER : Batch 2
loop Coder reruns
CODER --> TL : Handoff attempt
TL -[#F59E0B]> TL : Reject\ncheckstyle/report/smoke/health gaps
TL -> CODER : Retry
end

TL -> REV : Phase 2 first pass
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : PASS in chat
TL -[#DC2626]> TL : Red card\nartifact not updated on disk
TL -> REV : Reviewer rerun
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS on disk
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Final sign-off
end

@enduml
